<tr><td>author</td><td><a class="list" href="/gitweb/ffmpeg.git/search/92233a63444001477acb70f2afa43a05f10b5fd5?s=Michael+Niedermayer;st=author" title="Search for commits authored by Michael Niedermayer">Michael Niedermayer</a> <a class="list" href="/gitweb/ffmpeg.git/search/92233a63444001477acb70f2afa43a05f10b5fd5?s=michael@niedermayer.cc;st=author" title="Search for commits authored by michael@niedermayer.cc">&lt;michael@niedermayer.cc&gt;</a></td><td rowspan="2"></td></tr>
